Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are far stronger than the \Ninformation I gathered would imply...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...find Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps his feelings for his friends \Nstrengthened his magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You joined a splendid guild, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Charging towers are in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No anomalies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating transference lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing magic power compressors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning target status updates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Space-time coordinates set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we charge the elements?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until merger is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry calculating the compression!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Square, prepare for transfer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Preliminary movement, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning elemental merger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain's effect on wavelength, large!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recalculating space-time coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... I can't move a finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I used up too \Nmuch of my magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like Juvia can move either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our butts licked good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, someone's collapsed over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're not enemies anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I'd like to \Nsay, but I'm too scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical power 60% charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion elements 47% merged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,27 minutes until arrival above target!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think we'd be pressured \Ninto this course of action
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,while the Council Chair is ailing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While the Chair is absent, it is us 9 who are \Nresponsible for the stability of the magical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry so much, Org.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we are attacking another \Ncountry with magic unprovoked,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we can justify it under clause 27, paragraph \N4 of the National Security and Safety Act!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a matter of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to fire Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:59.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zeref who is the true evil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only pray that Etherion will \Nbe our saving grace and destroy Zaref!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long, Lord Sieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream you've had for 8 \Nyears will become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not afraid, Ultear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I always have complete \Nfaith in you, Lord Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so. There is \Nno danger to your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am shaking a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail, then I will be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is very much worth \Nrisking one's life for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another 25 minutes, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Siegrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trick us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am named Ikaruga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way! Who is this crazy broad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Aren't you unrefined?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Imposs... ible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing which I cannot cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, some street performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I severed your nerves without \Ncutting your clothes or flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the essence of the New Moon School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that is where you were, Miss Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not an opponent you can defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... That card is protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way anything from \Nthe outside could harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not a normal sword she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... Believe in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She sliced through the spatial divide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:18.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, your sword made \Ndistortions in this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I managed to cut my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword that can cut through the \Nspatial divide is amazing enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but to use the enemy's slices \Nin that split second...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Titania's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called yourself Ikaruga, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In lieu of an introduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you perhaps not see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That at which you gaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...beyond the mist, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a mononoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying so hard to find Jellal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you no longer see the flash \Nof swords all around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes... Those are the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting serious now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:21.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no mere passerby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel, Circle Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,New Moon School.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the swords were...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,New Moon School.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Garuda Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Empress Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That armor has the ability to \Ndefend against flames, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do well to requip in such an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't let his lordship \Nsee you looking like that, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do? Will you don \Nyour strongest armor soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best repent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Purgatory Armor, Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one that can stand \Nwhen faced with this visage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your strongest armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not yet understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what armor you don, \Nyou cannot win against my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She can't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's that armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, it's some outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit is nothing but cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so little of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to have a lot of \Nstrong armor left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strength is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like being by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uncomfortable around other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you crying all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before my eyes, countless numbers of \Nmy friends have become sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to protect those dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be seen as strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shut my own crying heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...inside of my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wear armor because I am weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never take it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cut down my opponents, \Neven if they are naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that the armor would protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That armor blocked the space that separates \Npeople's hearts from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail taught me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It taught me how close people are to \None another... How warm they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am lost no longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will turn my entirety to \Nstrength and have at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You really are amazing, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you unharmed, Sho?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've lost \Nsince I entered the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you and Jellal will all lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,15 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will rain down from the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That poem is dreadful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she talking about Etherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, take Simon and the others plus \Nall the people from Fairy Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and get away from this tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do as I ask, Sho?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:19.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember I was caught by some \Nweird moving vehicle and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You can't get nausea from memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that you were eaten by Fukuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Gray had to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gray took a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, you got fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That cat is taking him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Square?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll be caught by the Fiore army!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be better than \Ngetting hit by Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships are leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look below you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one we came in on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost, and Gray won?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't really lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna hold this over me for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really petty like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge! I'll fight that birdbrain \Nagain and get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An old friend of Erza's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Nice to meetcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wally sent me a message before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:43.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he found Lucy and Juvia collapsed, \Nalong with a defeated member of Trinity Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't know what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so they took your two \Nfriends outside the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't these the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Simon said they're our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, why is she tying \Nme up and dragging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've already been contacted by Sho \Nthat Trinity Raven have all been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is Jellal himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is heading toward him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is trying to end this all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have been connected \Nby fate for 8 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their destiny may be to do battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However Jellal is too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Save Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The game is already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is playing with people's \Nlives so fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Birth and death, after all, are the \Norigin and focus of all emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:54.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or to put it the other way around, \Nnothing is more boring than living on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will liberate my past friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower of Heaven has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it will be destroyed \Nin less than 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak of Etherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such confidence... So it was a bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion will rain down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that makes me feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:34.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can delay you by 10 minutes, \Nthen this will all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be annihilated as Zeref's sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Turn the ship around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Erza is still inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Natsu, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave her to just Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon is also with him... \NThey'll handle it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Turn the boat around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to save Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, there's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you? I want to go back, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no point...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion will fire any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that Natsu will bring Erza back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Simon told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:42.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Salamander's true power \Nawakens, even Jellal wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you aren't going \Nto save Erza, your comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza needs to defeat her own enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I should butt in to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza cannot win against Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about power or magic here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:12.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is still trying to save Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that she could \Nnever truly hate Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He will use those emotions of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that the Council is trying to \Nfire Etherion on this location, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, every human in \Nthis tower will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Sho's message, \Nwe only have 10 more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She headed to face him alone after \Ntelling everyone to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Erza well, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to believe it, but she may be \Ntrying to use Etherion to take Jellal with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me that first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Erza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven more minutes and \NEtherion will rain down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun for the \Nnext seven minutes, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I fear nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Etherion comes, I will \Nbe satisfied to take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally finished the tower, and now \Nyou're destroying it? Don't you care, Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:53.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pillar or two are nothing but decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:58.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho and the others believed in you for \Neight years to make those decorations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining about \Nevery little thing I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is the R-system. \NThese eight years were for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that... is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:22.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem you have improved a \Nbit, but I guess that's your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Ms. Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you get scared sometimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on your side, no matter what Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, we're the strongest team!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you, Erza. I always \Ndid for these past 8 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd told you... \NRight now, I fear nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the same Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:24:00.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Satellite-something everyone's \Nso worried about is what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Square! And why don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely powerful destructive spell \Nthat can destroy an entire city easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're in deep trouble \Nif we get hit by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: A Prayer Under the Holy Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:20.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do! Where is Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that Natsu gets some common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:26.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
